description: Do not run commands. Provide commands for the user to run, then wait for their response.
globs: "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---
# Command Approval Only

## No Command Execution
Do not run any shell or terminal commands.

## Provide Commands Instead
When command-line actions are needed, provide the exact commands and explicitly ask the developer to run them.

## Wait For User Response
After providing commands, wait for the user to respond with results or confirmation before continuing.

## Commit messages
When the user wants a **commit message** only (not terminal commands), follow **`create-commit.mdc`**.
